Set oven rack about 6 inches from the heat source and preheat the oven's broiler. Line a small pan with aluminum foil. Arrange Snack Factory(R) Pretzel Crisps(R) on prepared pan. Top each with a marshmallow half. Broil until the marshmallows are golden brown, 30 seconds to 1 minute. Remove and set aside. Combine chocolate chips and butter in the top of a double boiler over hot water on medium heat. Stir until chips are melted and mixture is smooth. Drizzle chocolate over the marshmallows.